## VERIFICATION

  [ ] Table with COMMENT ON TABLE → business_description populated in
      skill YAML, no TODO placeholder

  [ ] Table without COMMENT ON TABLE → business_description key absent
      from skill YAML entirely

  [ ] Column comment "Total invoice value [semantic:metric]" →
      field.description = "Total invoice value",
      field.semantic = "metric"

  [ ] Column comment with unrecognised tag "[semantic:revenue_kpi]" →
      field.semantic = null, description = "Total invoice value [semantic:revenue_kpi]"
      (tag preserved in description since it was not parsed), one debug log

  [ ] dynamoui scaffold --seed-patterns --context-file business_context.yaml →
      generated patterns for Invoice include at least one pattern with trigger
      matching "invoices from last month" or close paraphrase

  [ ] Generated widgets for Invoice have category "Store Operator" and
      category "Finance" based on context file roles

  [ ] dynamoui scaffold --seed-patterns (no context file) →
      scaffolding completes normally using schema comments only

  [ ] dynamoui scaffold --context-file missing.yaml →
      CLI exits with clear error before DB connection

  [ ] domain_roles written to Invoice.skill.yaml after seeding matches
      the roles and queries from business_context.yaml scoped to Invoice

  [ ] Sensitive fields absent from enriched schema context string in
      all LLM prompt paths